               Confined Three Months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ROWBOTTOM - <rs id="t18210718-58-verdict340" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210718-58-verdict340" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210718-58-verdict340" type="verdictSubcategory" value="manslaughter"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 22.</p>
